column5: Just wondering if anyone can tell me if you can do any fishing at Dundas Valley Conservation?
If it's for trout then obviously not.
is that bronte creek or 16 mile? bronte at dundas MAY have an extended fall season for trout and salmon.
Bronte at dundas does but I am not sure if only south of the road. check the regs.
Whatcha looking to fish for in Dundas?  You can fish anywhere, just depends if there are fish there or what you are targeting...  Burt
